Good work Igbert. You put together the charming guide I always wanted to make.  <P>I have one bit to add.  Watch out for this bug if you use memory blur or enthrall:<P>Blurring near-dead creatures too far from thier spawn point will sometimes make them teleport home.  An example is spirocs in timorous, who will blink back to the birdhouse if you pull them beyond the south rocks, beat them up, then mem blur them.<P>
