Sulla Khai,<P>The Frost Giant scouts are almost invariably my target. Their MR seems pretty low. I did not have to even tash them. The prey of the Frost Giant Scouts would be dire wolves. A frost giant can kill a dire wolf in about 45 seconds, and there are plenty of dire wolves.<P>This works from 36 or so all the way to 44. Great stuff.<P>Xenno, at around level 30 I didn't charm solo. Although Igbert seems to beleive that Griffens (the mid 20s version) would be pretty good. While there are plenty in NK, I do not know what you would sick them on.<P>Perhaps overthere would be a better bet. Once you reach 36 or 37, go to iceclad it is simply amazing (as long as it does not get nerfed!).<BR>
